{"word":"G1291 - διαστέλλομαι - diastéllomai - dee-as-tel'-lom-ahee - Charge","slug":"G1291","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διαστέλλομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>diastéllomai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>dee-as-tel'-lom-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Charge"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B4;&#x03B9;&#x03B1;&#x03C3;&#x03C4;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03BB;&#x03BB;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9; - diastellomai</b> - <i>dee-as-tel'-lom-ahee</i><p/>Middle voice from <a href=\"#/G1223\">G1223</a> and <a href=\"#/G4724\">G4724</a>; to <i>set</i> (oneself) <i>apart</i> (figuratively <i>distinguish</i>), that is, (by implication) to <i>enjoin:</i> - charge, that which was (give) commanded (-ment)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1293\">G1293</a>, <a href=\"#/G1989\">G1989</a>, <a href=\"#/G1992\">G1992</a>, <a href=\"#/G2687\">G2687</a>, <a href=\"#/G2689\">G2689</a>, <a href=\"#/G4724\">G4724</a>, <a href=\"#/G4958\">G4958</a>, <a href=\"#/G5288\">G5288</a>, <a href=\"#/G5289\">G5289</a>"}]}